long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1148204 Screencast showing erratic scrollbar drawing
Description of problem: LibreOffice scroll bars are not drawn correctly.
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): libreoffice-base-5.1.2.1-4.fc24.x86_64 gtk3-3.20.3-1.fc24.x86_64
How reproducible: Always
Steps to Reproduce: 1. Open libreoffice writer 2. Scroll up and down and watch the scroll bar
Actual results: The scroll bar is drawn incorrectly in a way which makes it impossible to tell the current scroll position from looking at it.
Expected results: The scroll bar is drawn normally.
This worked this morning, so recent gtk3 triggered this I assume. I bet its the same thing that affected another theme which I have fixed for next 5-1 upstream. Lets try a backport of that.
